								"editorData": [
									{
										"data": [
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "AnimationTags"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[ChristianD] When the PLYR is easing out from the pain, the PLYR looks towards the sigil and noticed there's a lower arm out of the sigil looking for something to hold on. Then the hand opens up looking for help."
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "Attitude"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Default"
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "(Cine) Next, in the centre of the sparks, you suddenly see a hand and lower arm coming out of the sigil. The hand opens and closes, looking for something to hold on to. A voice resounds, or so it seems, from deep within the stone."
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicObjects"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
